long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Privacy is crucial for sensitive searches. PrivateSearch helps maintain your privacy by providing secure search options directly from the address bar. 
You can use commands to search with private search engines. 

For example:
- @duck pregnancy test
- @qwant insurance policy
The default search is powered by Yahoo.

Learn more:  https://private.kidsmode.app/
